data.description: Caledonia custom-built previously featured Parade of Homes 5 bed + office 4 bath home on 2+ acres in the exclusive Lake Ridge Estates.  4 stall attached garage.  This property is setup for entertaining inside and out!  Check out the 2 year new large saltwater pool with smart (or manual) controlled fountains and multiple lighting options with a $20,000 safety auto cover to keep kids and pets safe. Patio is pre-plumbed for future slide, has inlay for patio umbrellas and volleyball net or basketball hoop.  Inviting pavilion in private backyard... with plenty of room for future outbuilding.  This home features large open spaces, and a luxurious gourmet kitchen with oversized granite island, ample storage and counter space, and walk-in pantry.  Welcoming family room with fireplace and custom built-ins.  Main floor owner's suite with lighted box tray ceiling, gorgeous tiled shower, whirlpool jacuzzi tub, and large walk-in closet.  Upper level with 2 beds with walk-in closets, and a bath.  Rec room with double-sided fireplace, full kitchen w/ beer tap, and plenty of space for fun.  In-home gym with minifridge, counter, and exhaust.  Lower level bedroom or office with fireplace.  Tons of storage in this home.  All the features and quality you'd expect.   Experience the pinnacle of luxury living in this exquisite residence - your dream home awaits.  See feature list attached to listing.
